    Enumeration of button types.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BUTTON
      Buttons of type BUTTON use actions represented in the event onClick by javascript.
      IMAGE
      Buttons of type IMAGE use actions represented in the event onClick by javascript and the button is represented by a image.
      RESET
      Buttons of type RESET clean the form elements values to default values.
      SUBMIT
      Buttons of type SUBMIT send the form elements values by POST or GET.
